

Geometry

  CT includes 
   Support tube: from 40 cm to ..

  CT sensitive region 
   R from 45 cm to 155cm. ( Lever arm of 110 cm)
   Number of layer is 50.  Each layer has 2.2 cm thickness.

  Position of Outer Support tube.
  

 
Default value in J4ParameterList
  
  fSupportTubInnerR = 40*cm;                  // InnerR of Support Tub
  fSupportTubOuterR = 44*cm;                  // OuterR of Support Tub

  fCDCOuterR  = 157cm
  fCDCHalfZ   = 160cm

  
   